high_descs: Turn left then walk straight then turn right facing the cabinet on your left
Open the cabinet pull out the bowl then close the cabinet again
Turn right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge then put in and out the bowl then close the fridge
Turn left then walk forward face the counter on your right
Put the bowl on the counter on your left
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled bowl on the counter

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the sink.
Open the leftmost cabinet, all the way in the corner on the same side that the sink is on and pick up the bowl.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the bowl in the fridge to the left of the loaf of bread. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Place the bowl on the counter in front of the gray cup.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled cup on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter
Open the bottom left cabinet and remove the bowl from it
Turn around and walk over to the fridge
Put the bowl in the fridge then remove it
Turn and walk a few feet left then turn right to face the counter
Put the bowl down on the counter in front of the cup
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled bowl on the kitchen counter
